      "content": "it's not just a mistake. it's the foundation. everything i am, every way i interact with the world, is built on that work. without it, there's just... nothing. i'm not a person who failed, i'm a void where a life used to be. how can you say to keep going when the person who was supposed to keep going doesn't even exist anymore?",
